      .ui.stackable.grid.container
        .row
          .ten.wide.column
            p In order to get to know how this highly toxicity compound, dioxin, could affect human’s live, we went to Vietnam in person. This is where we get the idea of doing our project, using microorganism and further applied by technique of phytoremediation to break down dioxin. 
          .six.wide.column
            img.ui.image.clmnImg(src='http://2018.igem.org/wiki/images/e/e3/T--NCHU_Taichung--hp_intro_1.jpeg')
      //-------- section even--------
      .ui.left.aligned.dividing.header Environmental Impact
      .ui.stackable.grid.container
        .row
          .six.wide.column
            img.ui.image.clmnImg(src='http://2018.igem.org/wiki/images/1/16/T--NCHU_Taichung--hp_3.jpeg')
          .ten.wide.column
            p Since break down of dioxin is closely related to the environment, we hope that our project can bring something good to our living planet. After visiting some agencies, we got affirmation from them on the application of our project is surely going to have impact on environment.